Version History:

v1.0.0 (Initial Release) - June 2025
- Core allocation algorithms and fairness implementations
- Basic zero-knowledge proof system integration
- Lean 4 theorem proving framework
- Initial documentation and examples

v1.1.0 (Entropy Fairness Update) - July 2025  
- Added entropy-based fairness duality algorithms
- Enhanced ZK proof system with Halo2 integration
- Expanded theoretical framework with convergence proofs
- Improved performance and scalability

v1.2.0 (Multi-Domain Support) - August 2025
- Healthcare allocation domain implementation
- Multi-resource allocation algorithms
- Advanced privacy-preserving protocols
- Comprehensive benchmarking suite

v1.2.3 (Current) - September 2025
- Bug fixes and performance improvements
- Enhanced documentation and tutorials  
- Community contribution guidelines
- Stability and usability enhancements

