ACTION, ARISING OUT OF OR IN CONNECTION WITH THE USE OR PERFORMANCE OF THIS
SOFTWARE.

The allocation algorithms and fairness measures provided in this software are
based on mathematical models and assumptions. Real-world applications may
require additional considerations, domain expertise, and validation. Users are
responsible for ensuring the appropriateness and safety of applications in
their specific contexts.

The cryptographic implementations are provided for research and educational
purposes. While efforts have been made to follow best practices, users should
conduct their own security audits for production deployments and consult with
cryptographic experts when implementing privacy-critical applications.

